liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Raheem Sterling beats the challenge of the covering Spurs defence and muscles the ball home off the keeper. But did he use his arm in the build up? And is there a problem brewing for Cristian Romero? Did he lash out at Thiago Silva after the Brazilian clattered into him to win the ball in the first place? That's been brushed over, Chelsea has their goal ruled out and the crowd are really up now.
